 \mathrm{sign}(x)\left(e^{|x|}-1\right)+C 
 \mathrm{sign}(x)\left(e^{|x|}-1\right)+C=\left\{\begin{array}{} e^x-1+C&\text{if }x\ge0\\ 1-e^{-x}+C&\text{if }x\lt0\\ \end{array}\right. 
